item.title: Help me! need realy help!
item.dc:creator: @Liquid_Magic Liquid Magic
item.description:
@Liquid_Magic wrote:

Rofl, that’s not the way of adding custom items…it’s client sided…check out the “Modules” board, you’ll find some useful and very nice customs there.

Meh, but with your “problem”, item.cfg is for editing previous item examines or bonuses, even id’s but it usually fucks up the item itself, unless you’re using a Winterlove source.

Like I said, check out the modules board.
